text: == Events == * Battle of Brunanburh: King Athelstan of England defeats the Viking king of Dublin, the Scots, and Strathclyde. * September 21 – Magdeburg becomes capital of the Holy Roman Empire. == Births == * Duke William IV of Aquitaine * Gu Hongzhong == Deaths == * July 11 – King Rudolph II of Burgundy * July 14 – Duke Arnulf I of Bavaria Category:930s
